    <title>Solution to the King Meta</title>
    <link>https://fol-archive.netlify.app/t/solution-to-the-king-meta/71367</link>
    <description>As you all propably know, the new king meta forces evils to prepare fake and scummy logs , while forcing BD such as hunters and princes to claim to a possibly evil king, which harms the BD&#39;s interests. The evil king can namely find an ally and whisper them who the prince is. As a result, this meta must be stopped. 

What I propose is the removal of the whisper ability from the king. Thus the Good King cannot detect fake claims and the Evil King cannot find prince, nor let evils know they are allied with the king. This allows for smarter play by the king who has to protect his allies without them knowing that. A public implication is always possible.

In reality, kings are a kingdom&#39;s leader and should not have anything to hide or whisper.

Please comment on my idea to stop the horrible meta and ,if you want me to, I will  
edit the post including the reworked king&#39;s class card.</description>
    
